headline: URBAN OUTFITTERS IS SHOWING UP EVERYWHERE YOU ARE, MAKING THE HOLIDAYS EASIER, MORE FUN, AND FULL OF MAXED-OUT JOY FROM CHICAGO O'HARE TO NYC
summary: Urban Outfitters continues its "Everything, Everywhere, All You Want" holiday campaign with a debut of Club Holiday pop-up experiences, showing up inside Chicago O'Hare International Airport and in New York City. Each activation transforms high-traffic spaces into vibrant moments designed to help customers pause, play, and tap into the spirit of the season.

headline: Tegra Recognized as Core Factory Partner at Nike's "2025 Global Factory Partner Summit"
summary: Tegra, the sportswear manufacturing company of Sae-A Trading, was formally recognized as a core factory partner at Nike's "2025 Global Factory Partner Summit," underscoring its elevated role within Nike's global supply network.
